our%20luck%20against%20the%20Neller%20bot.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3E%3Cstrong%3EGoing%20to%20Boston%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20-%20three%20throws%2C%20keep%20the%20highest%20each%20time.%20Five%20rounds.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3E%3Cstrong%3EDrop%20Dead%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20-%20five%20dice%2C%20twos%20and%20fives%20kill%2C%20any%20kill%20voids%20the%20throw.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3E%3Cstrong%3EShip%2C%20Captain%2C%20Crew%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20-%20collect%20a%206%2C%20then%20a%205%2C%20then%20a%204.%20The%20remaining%202%20dice%20are%20cargo.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3E%3Cstrong%3EFarkle%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20-%20six%20dice%2C%20combo%20scoring%2C%20push%20your%20luck.%20First%20to%2010%2C000.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3E%3Cstrong%3ESevens%20Out%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20-%202d6%2C%20sum%20to%20score%2C%20but%20any%207%20wipes%20the%20turn.%20First%20to%2050.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3E%3Cstrong%3ECee-lo%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20-%203d6%20street%20game.%204-5-6%20wins%2C%201-2-3%20loses%2C%20trips%20and%20points%20fight%20for%20the%20rest.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Ch2%20id%3D%22built-with%22%3EBuilt%20with%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3E%3Cstrong%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%22https%3A%2F%2Fthreejs.org%22%3EThree.js%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20-%20WebGL%20rendering%20for%20the%20scene%2C%20dice%2C%20lights%2C%20and%20post-processing.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3E%3Cstrong%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%22https%3A%2F%2Fgithub.com%2Fpmndrs%2Fcannon-es%22%3Ecannon-es%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20-%20rigid-body%20physics%20for%20every%20roll%2C%20simulated%20in%20a%20Web%20Worker.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3E%3Cstrong%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%22https%3A%2F%2Fpolyhaven.com%22%3EPoly%20Haven%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20-%20CC0%20PBR%20textures%20for%20the%20felt%2C%20wood%2C%20slate%2C%20and%20tray%20surfaces.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3E%3Cstrong%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%22https%3A%2F%2Fkenney.nl%2Fassets%2Fcasino-audio%22%3EKenney%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20-%20CC0%20dice%20SFX.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3E%3Cstrong%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%22https%3A%2F%2Fgohugo.io%22%3EHugo%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20-%20static%20site%2C%20content%20routing%2C%20and%20the%2